channel.title: I need help
channel.description: hi guys! :) i saw a video on you tube that showed a guy on moparscape bringing up a list that had items on it with a code beside them. he then immediately got the item in his inventory by doing something. i have found the list but i dont no wat to do with the chat. can sum1 nice plz help??? thx!!!!!! :D

item.title: I need help
item.dc:creator: @jarrell1022 jarrell1022
item.description:
@jarrell1022 wrote:

type in (in moparscape) ::item (4 digit item code) ex. ::item 4151 (spawns an whip on the floor)
or for an item direcly in ur inv its ::pickup (4 digit item code) (amount) ex. ::pickup 4151 1 (pickups 1 whip)

ur welcome
